    • Constructor Detail

      • Knowledge

        public Knowledge(java.lang.String name,
                 java.lang.String id,
                 int intPriority,
                 ImprovementCollaborator leader,
                 Request approvedRequest,
                 int intImpactedCommunity,
                 int intType)

        Knowledge

        Description: Constructs a new Knowledge object with the specified name, ID, priority, leader, approved request, impacted community, and type. The intImpactedCommunity is changed to a Community using Community.intToCommunity(int). The intType is changed into a type of KnowledgeType project using KnowledgeType.intToKnowledgeType(int)

        Preconditions:

        • The name parameter must be a String representing the name of the knowledge.
        • The id parameter must be a String representing the ID of the knowledge.
        • The intPriority parameter must be an integer representing the priority of the knowledge (1 for urgent, 2 for high, 3 for medium, and 4 for low).
        • The leader parameter must be an ImprovementCollaborator object representing the leader of the knowledge.
        • The approvedRequest parameter must be a Request object representing the approved request associated with the knowledge.
        • The intImpactedCommunity parameter must be an integer representing the impacted community of the knowledge (1 for Students, 2 for Professors, 3 for Administrative).
        • The intType parameter must be an integer representing the type of knowledge (1 for Standarization, 2 for Documentations, 3 for Optimization).

        Postconditions:

        • A new Knowledge object is created with the provided name, ID, priority, leader, approved request, impacted community, and type.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the knowledge.
        id - The ID of the knowledge.
        intPriority - The int which represents a level of priority of the Knowledge project .
        leader - The leader of the knowledge.
        approvedRequest - The approved request associated with the knowledge.
        intImpactedCommunity - The int which represents an impacted community of the knowledge.
        intType - The int which represents a type of knowledge project.
